            "199: ## 7. Working Log Extensions (Internal)",
            "200: ",
            "201: These are internal implementation details not part of the serialized authorship note, but affect what data is available for building `change_history`.",
            "202: ",
            "203: ### WorkingLogEntry — New fields",
            "204: ",
