            "206: |-------|------|-------------|",
            "207: | `added_line_ranges` | `Vec<(u32, u32)>` or null | 1-based inclusive ranges of added lines in new-content coordinates |",
            "208: | `deleted_line_ranges` | `Vec<(u32, u32)>` or null | 1-based inclusive ranges of deleted lines in old-content coordinates |",
            "209: | `added_line_entries` | `Vec<(u32, String)>` or null | (line_number, content) pairs for each added line |",
