            "223: ",
            "224: ## 8. Line History Command (Entirely New)",
            "225: ",
            "226: New CLI command for tracing the authorship history of a specific line.",
            "227: ",
            "228: ### Usage",
            "229: ",
            "230: ```",
            "231: git-ai line-history <file> <line> [--commit <sha>]",
            "232: ```",
            "233: ",
            "234: ### Algorithm",
            "235: ",
            "236: 1. Read line content at the specified commit.",
            "237: 2. `git log -L<line>,<line>:<file>` to find all commits touching that line.",
            "238: 3. For each commit, read authorship note and `change_history`.",
            "239: 4. Walk backward through checkpoints using line mapping to determine which checkpoint introduced/modified the line.",
            "240: ",
            "241: ### Line mapping functions",
            "242: ",
            "243: - `reconstruct_diff_ops()` — Rebuilds interleaved Equal/Delete/Insert operations from separate added/deleted range lists.",
            "244: - `map_new_to_old()` — Maps new-file line number to old-file position; `None` if the line was inserted.",
            "245: - `reverse_through_insert()` — When a line is in an Insert range, finds old-file position of what was replaced.",
            "246: - `find_checkpoints_that_touched_line()` — Walks checkpoints in reverse, tracking line position through each diff.",
            "247: ",
            "248: ### Output schema",
            "249: ",
            "250: ```json",
            "251: {",
            "252:   \"file\": \"string\",",
            "253:   \"line\": \"integer\",",
            "254:   \"at_commit\": \"string\",",
            "255:   \"line_content\": \"string\",",
            "256:   \"history\": [",
            "257:     {",
            "258:       \"commit_sha\": \"string\",",
            "259:       \"commit_date\": \"string\",",
            "260:       \"commit_message\": \"string\",",
            "261:       \"target_line\": \"integer\",",
            "262:       \"checkpoints\": [",
            "263:         {",
            "264:           \"timestamp\": \"integer\",",
            "265:           \"kind\": \"string\",",
            "266:           \"agent_type\": \"string | null\",",
            "267:           \"model\": \"string | null\",",
            "268:           \"prompt_id\": \"string | null\",",
            "269:           \"prompt_text\": \"string | null\",",
            "270:           \"line_content\": \"string | null\",",
            "271:           \"additions\": \"integer\",",
            "272:           \"deletions\": \"integer\"",
            "273:         }",
            "274:       ]",
            "275:     }",
            "276:   ]",
            "277: }",
            "278: ```",
