            "282: ## 9. Cursor Integration Extensions (Entirely New)",
            "283: ",
            "284: ### Workspace-composer map",
            "285: ",
            "286: Scan `~/.cursor/User/workspaceStorage/*/` to map conversation IDs to workspace paths. ",
            "287: ",
            "288: ### Conversation workspace root fallback",
            "289: ",
